    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1867-06-21T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1867-06-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="261" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d261">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. F. W. Seward</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. Dix</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 85.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1867-06-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 21, 1867.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I have to acknowledge the receipt of your
                            despatches Nos. 85 and 86, both of which relate to the telegraphic
                            communication sent by you to this department at the special request of
                            the Emperor in behalf of Maximilian.</p>
                <pb facs="0321" n="253" xml:id="pg_253"/>
                <p>In connection with this subject it may be well to inform you that nothing
                            is omitted that could be done properly, and it is done in the way that
                            seemed likely to be useful.</p>
                <p>I am, sir, your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>F. W. SEWARD, <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary,</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">John A. Dix</hi>, Esq., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>., &amp;<hi rend="italic">c</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
